  <brief_title>A Phase 3 Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Triple Therapy With CJ-12420 in H. Pylori Positive Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Randomized, Double-blind, Active-controlled, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of a Triple Therapy With CJ-12420, Amoxicillin and Clarithromycin in H. Pylori Positive Patients</official_title>
